nodes.text: Resdox was a human male who held the rank of Vice Admiral in the Resistance. In the year 34 ABY, he was present in the Resistance base on the planet D'Qar.
When the Resistance began evacuating the D'Qar base, Resdox was assigned to the medical frigate Anodyne.

Resdox was portrayed by James McGrath in Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens, and was first named in the film's credits. While he doesn't appear on-screen, it is noted in the Star Wars: The Last Jedi: The Visual Dictionary he is present with the Resistance Navy ships that participated in evacuating D'Qar after the events of The Force Awakens.
